ote><br />\n同中世紀獵巫一樣，人講就信<br />\n而家叫獵毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bd4c62abb59be23beb23a0c09551b3643d595d","tid":432920,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:11:27.000Z","msg":"五毛同屈毛都非常影響正常討論<br />\n一個就扭曲事實<br />\n一個就一睇到唔啱聽就屈人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7b2d6eb611304a8422c8ff729c3fecc4c1c44a","tid":432920,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f59fc0524d63493852df27523d85082272098aeb","tid":432920,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c38be0f3e2bd705c984f7613f74588bf7a16d0b","tid":432920,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"佢地太認真啦 <br />\n以為自己係網上不斷屈毛copy paste <br />\n就打擊到中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd33085a49d8632bfccca57e53002dd643d846d","tid":432920,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/213429_e7905e26025910dcd68cdb620f12877f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F213429_e7905e26025910dcd68cdb620f12877f.png&h=ab75533b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAdmin既意思係<br />\n你同班癲狗其實冇乜分別<br />\n出埋d 19 list叫人block邊個邊個<br />\n本身哩件事就係低智</blockquote><br />\n此言差矣，我份list有清楚講明資料僅供參考，你哋打算點做完全係你哋自己決定，而當時我亦無洗板式成個list連埋啲圖倒哂出嚟阻住人，高下立見就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"d03d789f7ab25b38eaf9536245c44ce80ee61272","tid":432920,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"584781ebcb64bebb44c970f0f883341444de9603","tid":432920,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb9f33303d7b7684a5dc2a82493a296e1ff31e5b","tid":432920,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/213429_e7905e26025910dcd68cdb620f12877f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F213429_e7905e26025910dcd68cdb620f12877f.png&h=ab75533b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAdmin既意思係<br />\n你同班癲狗其實冇乜分別<br />\n出埋d 19 list叫人block邊個邊個<br />\n本身哩件事就係低智</blockquote><br />\n此言差矣，我份list有清楚講明資料僅供參考，你哋打算點做完全係你哋自己決定，而當時我亦無洗板式成個list連埋啲圖倒哂出嚟阻住人，高下立見就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\nD阿婆渣住掌心雷投票夠係 資料僅供參考<br />\n你貼個list咪就係想人地跟住個list block<br />\n承認哩樣野好難咩？<br />\n宜家班人洗版犯緊板規就另一件事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你望過我份list未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我份list分類清晰，而並非單純歸類為五毛<br />\n<br />\n要圖有圖，要字有字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺呢個情形下，佢哋能夠有更多資訊參考同埋可以更冷靜咁考慮進一步應該點做，呢點絕不能與其他list相題並論"},{"pid":"53e21499626c4ff551cbd81be658e08fab3f19b3","tid":432920,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99b1965c5d3c7182a4c993c735444628b3b65031","tid":432920,"uid":71725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6d6580ad013737e5d56a2170bddbb3df43941dc","tid":432920,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike"